title: Good Omens | Killer Queen
author: purplefringe vids
comment: I really love agnes, like, she knew she was going to be killed no matter what but still decided to do it in the most extravagant way possible, while also getting rid of all the people who decided to killed her for very unfair reasons.
I swear Agnes just walking the people to burn her is a mood.

This is really good, there need to be more tributes for the other characters, as much as I love Aziraphale and Crowley.
The dramatic zoom on the hot cocoa tho... I lost it.
Finally, something about Agnes! She deserves this :) I love the ineffitable idiots, but others deserve some credit too :D
Finally an Agnes and Anathema centric fanvid! Killer Queen is a perfect song for those two. Great editing, I loved it!
